3690246543abe45be2cf6738bf4","tid":377033,"uid":54279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Gw2<br />\n細個跟Zerg 打wvw 上TS 聽鬼佬指揮，同鬼佬吹水<br />\n學左唔少英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWvwvw其實冇乜指揮成份 都係一條火車跟住行姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個玩gw2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎我真係老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4d3bac50cc6f96a78fe73640d7cef7c60ef2b7","tid":377033,"uid":15336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:46:24.000Z","msg":"真心 我覺得認真學既話 淨係睇美劇都夠晒做<br />\n我覺得oral係可以靠listening練返黎<br />\n我以前英文都差 係差到可以將cancel讀左做central<br />\n但之後開始煲美劇<br />\n而家唔敢講話幾好幾好<br />\n叫做流利 唔洗係腦入面用中文翻譯一次先<br />\n當你聽得多 你就可以聽得出自己講得好唔好 糾正返自己"},{"pid":"b0ee1eb8b94020a0ce994df510754b1f1ec24c2c","tid":377033,"uid":15336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Gw2<br />\n細個跟Zerg 打wvw 上TS 聽鬼佬指揮，同鬼佬吹水<br />\n學左唔少英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWvwvw其實冇乜指揮成份 都係一條火車跟住行姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個玩gw2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎我真係老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n突破盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過講下又講<br />\n我玩gw2果時差唔多大學畢業<br />\n我而家諗返起 個感覺又真係好似好耐好耐之前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965c74c5ff27aa7b7f99b18e48ebea4e028a0b4d","tid":377033,"uid":54279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Gw2<br />\n細個跟Zerg 打wvw 上TS 聽鬼佬指揮，同鬼佬吹水<br />\n學左唔少英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWvwvw其實冇乜指揮成份 都係一條火車跟住行姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個玩gw2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎我真係老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n突破盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過講下又講<br />\n我玩gw2果時差唔多大學畢業<br />\n我而家諗返起 個感覺又真係好似好耐好耐之前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同你差唔多，gw2出個陣我final year,依家都做左幾年野<br />\n<br />\n個陣入左個外國人公會，有係ts同d鬼佬開咪講英文，不過毒撚唔識埋堆，玩玩下都係做cdrom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc1795161bfac2875cdc9cb816d885bc4f3bd38","tid":377033,"uid":125382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"GW2唔錯的 劇情都唔算太深 傾計算易<br />\n不過世界觀太大 想明晒有點吃力"},{"pid":"6aaac6dd0df9619f25292c46eec839c0c40c074f","tid":377033,"uid":128921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:22:50.000Z","msg":"Csgo"},{"pid":"934e929c8ef09e268ade99df35fd4a7695c5cf0f","tid":377033,"uid":49074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T09:48:41.000Z","msg":"gw2"}]}